 r‚ÜêTest_UC_003(stopFlag batchFlag);‚éïTRAP;tempDir;config;res;rc;ref;msg
‚çù Exercise the user command "CreateProject" with just a path but without the flag
 ‚éïTRAP‚Üê(999 'C' '. ‚çù Deliberate error')(0 'N')
 r‚ÜêT._Failed

 tempDir‚Üê‚àÜGetFolderInTempDir(‚äÉ‚éïSI),'_1'
 (tempDir,'/cider.config')‚éïNCOPY(##.CiderConfig.HOME,'/TestData/cider.config.Foo')

 config‚Üê‚àÜGetJSON5 tempDir,'/cider.config'
